snippet.title: Backrooms: The Project - Video Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam today!
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2294230/Backrooms_The_Project

Twitter: https://twitter.com/BackroomsTP
Discord: https://discord.com/invite/9KvrWFc8
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/nightdriveinteractive/
Facebook: https://facebook.com/profile.php?id=100089664806809
Linktree: https://linktr.ee/nightdriveinteractive

Backrooms: The Project is an immersive first-person found footage horror adventure game. Explore the different levels of this mysterious liminal dimension known as the Backrooms, finding and utilizing items to aid you in your escape. Be careful though...you are not alone.

Music:

"Welcome to HorrorLand" Kevin MacLeod (incompetech.com)
